@page "/about"
@layout PublicLayout

<PageTitle>About Us - AdmissionPlex</PageTitle>

<section style="padding:120px 60px 80px;">
    <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-tag" style="color:var(--ap-primary);">About</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">About AdmissionPlex</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="padding:40px;">
            <p style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.8; color:var(--ap-text-muted); margin-bottom:24px;">
                AdmissionPlex is India's comprehensive admission and career guidance platform. We help students discover their ideal career paths through scientifically designed psychometric assessments, personalized AI-powered career guidance, and expert counsellor consultations.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.8; color:var(--ap-text-muted); margin-bottom:24px;">
                Our platform measures 10 interest dimensions and 7 aptitude categories to create a detailed career suitability profile. Each student receives a comprehensive report with recommended careers, IQ benchmarking, and actionable guidance.
            </p>

            <h3 style="font-family:var(--ap-font-display); font-size:24px; margin:32px 0 16px;">What we offer</h3>
            <div class="grid-2" style="gap:16px;">
                <div style="border-left:3px solid var(--ap-primary); padding-left:16px;">
                    <div style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;">Psychometric Testing</div>
                    <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--ap-text-muted);">Scientifically validated assessments across interest and aptitude dimensions.</div>
                </div>
                <div style="border-left:3px solid var(--ap-sky); padding-left:16px;">
                    <div style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;">AI Career Guidance</div>
                    <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--ap-text-muted);">Chat with our AI assistant for personalized career advice.</div>
                </div>
                <div style="border-left:3px solid var(--ap-coral); padding-left:16px;">
                    <div style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;">Expert Counselling</div>
                    <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--ap-text-muted);">Book 1-on-1 sessions with experienced career counsellors.</div>
                </div>
                <div style="border-left:3px solid var(--ap-gold); padding-left:16px;">
                    <div style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;">Cutoff Analytics</div>
                    <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--ap-text-muted);">Engineering college cutoff data across MHT-CET, JEE and more.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
